data.value:
Welcome to Code Wars!
Code Wars is a fun and simple way that can help you learn the basics of C# programming.
Code Wars presents you with 12 challenges. You have to do these challenges in a certain amount of time. The faster you do the challenge, the higher your socre. Before each challenge you will be told what to do. You will also be given hints (if it is enabled).
If your code is correct, you do the next challenge. If it is wrong, you will get the error that was caused and a hint to fix it.
To begin, select your difficulty level and additional options, then hit 'Start Game'!
